data.description: Welcome home to this charming three bedroom, two bath residence nestled on a spacious 5000+ sq ft lot in the desirable city of Livermore, CA. Boasting 1224 square feet of living space, this home is perfect for those seeking comfort and convenience. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting and light-filled living area, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample storage space, and a breakfast bar, making it a delightful space for cooking and dining. The three bedrooms offer comfort and privacy, with the primary bedroom featuring access to the back yard and spa. The additional bathroom is thoughtfully designed and serves the two other bedrooms. Step outside to the expansive backyard, providing endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment and entertainment. The generous lot size allows for potential expansion or additional landscaping, providing a fantastic opportunity for those with a green thumb. Located in a sought-after neighborhood in Spring Valley, this home offers easy access to wonderful schools, parks, shopping, and dining options. Commuters will appreciate the proximity to major highways. Don't miss the chance to make this charming home yours!
